=== #37 [MEDIUM] Keycloak password reset allows user enumeration
## Finding

The tbpro realm has resetPasswordAllowed set to true. Depending on Keycloak's response behavior, the password reset flow may reveal whether an email address is registered — enabling user enumeration.

