=== #36 [MEDIUM] No security headers (CSP, X-Frame-Options, HSTS, Referrer-Policy)
## Finding

The Django application does not set standard security headers:

- **No Content-Security-Policy** — XSS risk
- **No X-Frame-Options** hardening — clickjacking risk
- **No Referrer-Policy** — information leakage
- **No Permissions-Policy** — unnecessary browser API access
- **No SECURE_HSTS_SECONDS** — HSTS not enforced at the application layer

**Severity:** MEDIUM
**Location:** src/thunderbird_accounts/settings.py in [thunderbird/thunderbird-accounts](https://github.com/thunderbird/thunderbird-accounts)

