=== #35 [MEDIUM] Keycloak offline session idle timeout is 30 days
## Finding

Keycloak offline sessions have a 30-day idle timeout (offlineSessionIdleTimeout: 2592000). A compromised device retains valid session tokens for up to a month without user activity. For an email service, this significantly extends the window of account compromise.

**Severity:** MEDIUM
**Location:** keycloak/data/import/tbpro-realm.json in [thunderbird/thunderbird-accounts](https://github.com/thunderbird/thunderbird-accounts)

## Remediation

- [ ] Reduce offline session idle timeout to 7 days
- [ ] Consider requiring re-authentication for sensitive operations (password change, email alias management, custom domain setup)

