- Denial of service via resource exhaustion

**Severity:** HIGH
**Location:** src/thunderbird_accounts/settings.py in [thunderbird/thunderbird-accounts](https://github.com/thunderbird/thunderbird-accounts)

## Remediation

- [ ] Configure DRF throttle classes for API endpoints (AnonRateThrottle, UserRateThrottle)
- [ ] Add WAF rules on the ALBs with rate-based rules
