=== #24 [MEDIUM] Secrets Manager IAM policy uses wildcard pattern
## Finding

The IAM policy for Secrets Manager access uses the pattern `mailstrom/{stack}/stalwart.postboot.*`. This grants access to all current and future postboot secrets. If a new secret is added (even accidentally), all nodes can read it.

