=== #23 [MEDIUM] S3 blob bucket hardening gaps
## Finding

The S3 blob storage bucket is missing several defense-in-depth controls:

- **No Block Public Access** — the four `BlockPublicAccess` settings are not configured
- **No access logging** — no audit trail of object access
- **No MFA Delete** — objects and versions can be deleted without MFA
